            <title>[HBASE-7946] Support VLong counters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7946</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently &lt;tt&gt;increment&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;incrementColumnValue&lt;/tt&gt; operations only support 64-bit counters. Supporting &lt;tt&gt;VLong&lt;/tt&gt; counters would be useful in cases when the majority of counters would fit in less than 8 bytes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
